SHORTCUTS

R - rotation mode
S - scaling mode
G - movement mode
ARROW KEYS; PAGEUP & PAGEDOWN - moves, rotates or scales;
ALT + R - resets rotation of selected 3d objects.
ALT + S - resets scaling
CTRL + KEYS - increments/decrements angle by 90 degrees.
DEL - deletes selected assets
SHIFT + D - duplicates selected objects
A - select/deselect all
NUMPAD 5 - goes to ortho mode.
NUMPAD 7 - top view (ortho mode).
NUMPAD 3 - side view (ortho mode).
NUMPAD 1 - different side view.

X - rotation/translation/scaling in X axis
Y - rotation/translation/scaling in Y axis
Z - rotation/translation/scaling in Z axis

SHIFT + X - aligns selected object by first's X value
SHIFT + Y - aligns selected object by first's Y value
SHIFT + Z - aligns selected object by first's Z value
